s Rowing]]\n*[[Manchester University Boat Club]] [[Image:Manchester University Boat Club Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n*[[Newcastle University Boat Club]] [[Image:Newcastle University Boat Club Blade.svg|40px]]\n*[[University of Northampton Rowing Club]]\n*[[Northumbria University Boat Club]] [[Image:Northumbria University Boat Club Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n*[[Nottingham University Boat Club]] [[Image:Van Mildert Boat Club Blade.svg|40px]]\n*[[Nottingham Trent University Rowing Club]]\n*[[Oxford University Boat Club]] [[Image:Oxford University Boat Club.svg|40px]]\n*[[Oxford University Women's Boat Club]] [[Image:Oxford University Boat Club.svg|40px]]\n*[[Oxford University Lightweight Rowing Club]] [[Image:Oxford University Boat Club.svg|40px]]\n*[[Oxford University Women's Lightweight Rowing Club]] [[Image:Oxford University Boat Club.svg|40px]]\n{{hidden begin|border=#aaa 1px solid; width: 35em|title=Oxford colleges}}\n:*[[Balliol College Boat Club]] [[File:Balliol College Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Brasenose College Boat Club (Oxford)]] [[Image:Rowing Blade Black.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Christ Church Boat Club]] [[File:Christ Church Boat Club Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Corpus Christi College Boat Club (Oxford)]] [[File:Corpus Christi College Boat Club Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Exeter College Boat Club]] [[Image:Lady Margaret Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Green Templeton Boat Club]] [[Image:Green Templeton Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Hertford College Boat Club]] [[Image:Hertford College Boat Club Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Jesus College Boat Club (Oxford)]] [[Image:Jesus College Oxford Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Keble College Boat Club]] [[File:Keble College Boat Club Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Lady Margaret Hall Boat Club]] [[File:Lady Margaret Hall Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Linacre College Boat Club]] [[File:Linacre College Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Lincoln College Boat Club]] [[File:Lincoln Rowing Blade.svg|40px]]\n:*[[Magdalen College Boat Club]] [[Image: